<a data-tip="p$t$zhou-li" href="/people/zhou-li">周立</a>，<strong title="当时不杂" class="zu-question-my-bio">当时不杂</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="22">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$he-zi-xuan" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/he-zi-xuan" class="zg-link" title="贺子轩">贺子轩</a>、</span><span class="user-block">知乎用户、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$hyman-li" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/hyman-li" class="zg-link" title="hyman li">hyman li</a></span>
</span>


<a href="javascript:;" class="more"> 等人赞同</a>


