<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block">知乎用户、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$xie-xiao-qing-13" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/xie-xiao-qing-13" class="zg-link" title="谢小卿">谢小卿</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$wu-gui-ying-gai-man-man-pa" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/wu-gui-ying-gai-man-man-pa" class="zg-link" title="乌龟应该慢慢爬">乌龟应该慢慢爬</a></span>
